Rule 1: Testing Strategy
- Write unit tests for all critical functions
- Implement integration tests for API endpoints
- Use contract testing for smart contract functionality
- Maintain high test coverage for core business logic

Rule 2: Test Data Management
- Use fixtures for consistent test data
- Implement database seeding for testing
- Clean up test data after each test run
- Use separate test database environment

Rule 3: Automated Testing
- Run tests automatically on code changes
- Implement CI/CD pipeline for testing
- Use linting and code quality checks
- Monitor test results and coverage reports

Rule 4: Manual Testing
- Test all user flows manually before deployment
- Verify blockchain interactions work correctly
- Test error scenarios and edge cases
- Validate API responses and data integrity
